community.name: asklemmy
community.title: asklemmy
community.description:
A loosely moderated place to ask open ended questions

If your post is

1. Open ended 
2. Not offensive (At this point, I do not have the bandwidth to moderate partisan political discussions)
3. **Not regarding lemmy support** ([!lemmy_support@lemmy.ml](https://lemmy.ml/c/lemmy_support) )
4. not ad nauseam inducing (please make sure its a question that would be new to most members)
5. [An actual topic of discussion](https://lemmy.ml/post/1239589)

it’s welcome here!
